snippet.title: Cities: Skylines Airports Release Trailer | Available NOW! | Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
✈️ Airports is LIVE NOW! ✈️
Experience the wonders and logistics with the latest expansion for Cities: Skylines. Please have your boarding pass ready as you start to place and design your airport. Fasten your seatbelts and connect your airport to the city through bus, metro, and train stations. Place your items in the overhead compartments so that you can create cargo terminals connected to your airport complex while hauling in new goods and materials. We are now at the perfect altitude to begin enhancing your city's travel industry! Thank you for flying with us today!
Get Airports now, and connect your City to the world!
